<br>
<br>
I agree with you, and the epics are another example of that.  But what you have to consider is the game has changed quite abit since we initially started our characters, and the 'Vision' is gone.  There are many more classes than can solo now, than the times when Druids and Necros were considered the only classes that could solo.  Melee could never solo in the past as well as they can now.  Everyones received a soloing boost in some form, and that goes for almost every class but the classes that could already solo well from the start(Druids/Necros).  <br>
<br>
I know clerics want to feel needed or important, but no class should be required these days for anything as much as Clerics are for high end healing.  There should always be at least 1 substitute class but there arent for Clerics.  The reason always pointed out why a Cleric should be required in groups is because Clerics cant do much on their own(solo).  The idea of that needs to be broken by allowing other classes to makeup for that class to get an event started just makes more sense in terms of the enjoyability of the game for everyone.<br>
<br>
Plus, i see so many clerics these days, or being 2-boxed(ton of people have 2 box clerics), that its silly to 'want' to be one-dimensional.  You cant apply the original 'vision' of EQ to today, too much has changed especially in the direction EQ seems to be headed as of late. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaidonrufflefuzz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aidon Rufflefuzz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Bitter Druids<br>Leader</span><br>  Posts: 1349<br> <font color=#333399>(8/9/02 12:50:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=28115.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.engtong.com/Valoran/images/60x60/aidon60x60.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ....</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Druids were 'made', as one of the few soloing classes. Even VI has stated this. </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
